OOC: Tomorrow im going to camp. I will be there for 3 weeks.  Since this is a 
long time to leave my characters in limbo, i will be lending them, something 
i have never done before.  Here are the characters and who i'll be lending 
them to...

Torca, Sharpedge, Banzai-Tron, Godfather-  Soulstice
Cyclonus, Scourge, Hun-Grr- Jer
Ramjet, Dirge, Skywarp- Rudra
Starscream- Robo
Wheeljack- Airly
Hurricane, Sideswipe, Ratchet, Orion- Zardus

I may be able to go on tomorrow morning, so anyone who objects to taking one 
of my chars, or needs information about him, has till then.

--part1_66.127b9c7d.289f5b32_boundary
